Package com.rapidminer.belt.buffer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Buffers
    Utility methods for creating mutable temporary buffers.
    Buffers.InternalBuffers
    Buffer creation methods for internal access.
    CategoricalBuffer<T>
    Temporary random access buffer that can be used to define a CategoricalColumn.
    DateTimeBuffer
    Abstract super-class of buffers for date-time instances
    Int32CategoricalBuffer<T>
    Implementation of a CategoricalBuffer with category index format IntegerFormats.Format.SIGNED_INT32 that can hold Integer.MAX_VALUE many different categories.
    NumericBuffer
    Temporary random access buffer that can be used to define a Column.
    ObjectBuffer<T>
    Temporary random access buffer that can be used to define a Column of category Column.Category.OBJECT.
    TimeBuffer
    A buffer for time instances with nanosecond precision.
    UInt16CategoricalBuffer<T>
    Implementation of a CategoricalBuffer with category index format IntegerFormats.Format.UNSIGNED_INT16 that can hold 65535 different categories.
    UInt2CategoricalBuffer<T>
    Implementation of a CategoricalBuffer with category index format IntegerFormats.Format.UNSIGNED_INT2 that can hold 3 different categories.
    UInt4CategoricalBuffer<T>
    Implementation of a CategoricalBuffer with category index format IntegerFormats.Format.UNSIGNED_INT4 that can hold 15 different categories.
    UInt8CategoricalBuffer<T>
    Implementation of a CategoricalBuffer with category index format IntegerFormats.Format.UNSIGNED_INT8 that can hold 255 different categories.
